    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Shadow Sacrament: The Roots of Evil</strong></i> is a disturbing survival horror game set in the 19th century. You play as a detective, tormented by a recent loss, who must use his wits and instincts to unravel a gruesome crime and survive the unspeakable horrors lurking in an ancient, isolated monastery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/20fad060815b33d1e572b4ab0b2ce0e3.avif?t=1772071412\" width=640 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haunted by his grief, he seeks purpose in the pursuit of truth. Each solved enigma reveals more of the dark mystery that haunts the site, while intense combat against nightmarish creatures tests his resolve. With limited resources and relentless terror, <i>Shadow Sacrament</i> delivers a horror experience that will push your courage and skill to its limits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/aac3f4260b4867abcb53a7cc8a2ec283.avif?t=1772071412\" width=640 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VENTURE INTO THE UNKNOWN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Within the eerie confines of an ancient monastery, traverse perilous corridors, scouring every darkened corner for crucial clues and essential items. Each creak and flicker fuels your dread, as you edge closer to uncovering a terrifying mystery—or sealing your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/9c51b329ec85e44fc5983ea050d6cb63.poster.avif?t=1772071412\" width=628 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/9c51b329ec85e44fc5983ea050d6cb63.webm?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/9c51b329ec85e44fc5983ea050d6cb63.mp4?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNCOVER HIDDEN TRUTHS WITH CUNNING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smart use of tools and the ability to decipher codes and puzzles are crucial to advancing the story. A sharp mind uncovers hidden truths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/0334e078fd344d68145a3bd63f091981.poster.avif?t=1772071412\" width=628 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/0334e078fd344d68145a3bd63f091981.webm?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/0334e078fd344d68145a3bd63f091981.mp4?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FACE YOUR FEARS IN HEART-POUNDING BATTLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for relentless terror as you confront sinister threats that lurk in the shadows. Only strategic combat and unwavering courage will ensure your survival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/8af3c9899490a9062396e6a58e28857e.poster.avif?t=1772071412\" width=628 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/8af3c9899490a9062396e6a58e28857e.webm?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/8af3c9899490a9062396e6a58e28857e.mp4?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm yourself with a diverse arsenal of weapons and steel your nerves against the horrors that await. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/67f05cceece7da4ece2148e99113ae60.poster.avif?t=1772071412\" width=628 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/67f05cceece7da4ece2148e99113ae60.webm?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/67f05cceece7da4ece2148e99113ae60.mp4?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MANAGE YOUR SCARCE RESOURCES WISELY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Every decision counts as you strategize to survive and thrive in a world where every resource is precious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/23157db877c46295f6b7bea773f38b01.poster.avif?t=1772071412\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002550/extras/23157db877c46295f6b7bea773f38b01.webm?t=1772071412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handcrafted Pixel Art:</strong> Mesmerizing frame-by-frame animation breathes life into a chilling world of terror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Storytelling:</strong> Plunge into a haunting narrative teeming with unspeakable horrors and spine-chilling mysteries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Puzzles:</strong> Confront intricate puzzles that guard the sinister secrets of the monastery, testing your wit and nerve.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unrelenting Combat:</strong> Face relentless battles where each decision could mean life or death in a ruthless struggle against darkness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management:</strong> Scavenge and ration precious resources, vital for surviving the lurking terrors that haunt every shadow.</p></li></ul>",
